4 April 2013Members of the media are invited to the Post-SoNA media briefing of the Social Protection and Community Development Cluster. The Chairperson of the cluster, Minister of Social Development, Bathabile Dlamini and Minister of Women, Children and People with Disabilities, Lulama Xingwana will lead the briefing. The details are as follows: Date: Monday, 07 April 2014 Time: 13h00 (please note change of time) Venue: GCIS, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Frances Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria NB: There will be a video-link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town Kindly confirm attendance by email or SMS to: Shadi Baloyi (Pretoria) E-mail: Shadib@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 946 7136Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 904 3557 Enquiries: Lumka Oliphant on 083 484 8067 Issued by Government Communication and Information System